thivien.net/T%C3%B4-Th%E1%BB%A9c/author-ZsPeAEZWTH-jxxg2cYfLgg">Tô Thức</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Ph%C3%BAc-%C6%AFng-B%C3%ACnh/Ho%E1%BA%A1-B%C3%ACnh-Nam-ti%C3%AAn-sinh-%C4%91%E1%BB%81-Duy-t%C3%A2m-t%E1%BA%A1p-ch%C3%AD-nguy%C3%AAn-v%E1%BA%ADn/poem-9BN-eBZXDgTQ-qTm1bP0mw">Hoạ Bình Nam tiên sinh đề Duy tâm tạp chí nguyên vận - 和屏南先生題唯心雜誌原韻</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Ph%C3%BAc-%C6%AFng-B%C3%ACnh/author-eQ6wft6d1E9_uEITUaRRlg">Nguyễn Phúc Ưng Bình</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Mai-Nghi%C3%AAu-Th%E1%BA%A7n/M%E1%BB%99ng-%C4%91%C4%83ng-H%C3%A0-H%C3%A1n/poem-bmNJwADre1PTjLamg-id0w">Mộng đăng Hà Hán - 夢登河漢</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Mai-Nghi%C3%AAu-Th%E1%BA%A7n/author-LM0kb8TnwF3pXyZ2viD2Eg">Mai Nghiêu Thần</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%C3%A0o-Ti%E1%BB%81m/Quy-kh%E1%BB%A9-lai-t%E1%BB%AB/poem-sfHCqxaQ75Zp7Waf7a2TsA">Quy khứ lai từ - 歸去來辭</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%C3%A0o-Ti%E1%BB%81m/author-y4iJ6v3mYp-Z_KEorcHd_g">Đào Tiềm</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Li%E1%BB%85u-T%C3%B4ng-Nguy%C3%AAn/Th%E1%BA%A7n-ngh%E1%BB%87-Si%C3%AAu-S%C6%B0-vi%E1%BB%87n-%C4%91%E1%BB%99c-thi%E1%BB%81n-kinh/poem-tuxu4iLcF3xnXyRsWnEiqA">Thần nghệ Siêu Sư viện độc thiền kinh - 晨詣超師院讀禪經</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Li%E1%BB%85u-T%C3%B4ng-Nguy%C3%AAn/author-cFCa0wn9ZwJZJ5nwtlsQmQ">Liễu Tông Nguyên</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%E1%BB%A5c-Du/Tr%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Dng-t%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-t%C6%B0-k%E1%BB%B3-3-Ng%E1%BB%99-ph%C3%B9-sinh-y%E1%BA%BFm-ph%C3%B9-danh/poem-CE1EtYm-ARPQj5E8Cd7b3Q">Trường tương tư kỳ 3 (Ngộ phù sinh, yếm phù danh) - 長相思其三（悟浮生，厭浮名）</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%E1%BB%A5c-Du/author-6xOAUbKdWiBr-eAAn9zXQQ">Lục Du</a>)<br/></div>	</div>
